{"type": "article", "id": 27673, "title": "相机包", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-02T07:27:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152807kAEXnlyHOgBsxTw7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>创立于 2013 年的美国品牌 Black Anchor 一直都致力于创造高品质的配件，最近他们又推出了一款为相机所设计的背包。这款背包采用 Horween 皮革和蜡帆布手工制成，内部的空间不仅足以容纳拍摄或是日常所需的用品，还能根据需要分割空间。蜡帆布本身的防水效果也能让你在户外安心进行拍摄。这款背包目前还处于<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/tacomamfg/camera-bags-straps-and-accessories-made-in-usa\">众筹</a>阶段，早鸟价为 225 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021528044BlcRsw8oxbafV2C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152804Jwf5XNdQ8utYvHAZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152805nu01dHFMfsVtEmpz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50368189\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152805b3wdi14BVH9cLoMs.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}